 Luna Solis, 30, were arrested on suspicion of crimes including possession of a narcotic drug for sale, according to police.Court records didn’t list attorneys who could comment on behalf Lopez or Solis, who are from Phoenix.Two children in the vehicle were turned over to state child protection officials, police said.